{"tid":1528324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[五邑司徒浩]麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:51:20.000Z","uid":192947,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"69b8868eed47a49aafe99d820eacee30a665fa2d","tid":1528324,"uid":192947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:37:37.000Z","msg":"8月31號，琴晚黑警嘅所作所為大家有目共睹，我希望聽朝見到大家。<br />\n<br />\n由6月到呢一刻，發生過大大小小嘅事，我曾經都覺得過關我咩事，但係如果你到今時今日都仲係覺得關我撚事，你唔配做香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我唔單只希望見到五邑司徒浩嘅學生舊生，我希望其他學校其他人，都可以係自己嘅母校出席。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係呢刻 你冇藉口話唔關自己事</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZhaZDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZhaZDs.jpg&h=91bebed1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd79477486544010f47557edb51586943bb11589","tid":1528324,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7f3d6c79c901cc9d38d025bdf112951781311836","tid":1528324,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"我地需要你關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[推上熱門］［92 &amp; 93］中學生為我地上前線 我地一齊聲援中學生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1527952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1527952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VUpjiC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VUpjiC.jpg&h=9cea0167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"970ab190108d2c351a9de990d48f97f670e2f2fe","tid":1528324,"uid":192947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d43dc969cb6c51ec37f8303b4da51d72cf9858a6","tid":1528324,"uid":192947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;